<p>&nbsp;</p>                        
                                                    
                                                    <h2>Activities</h2>
                                                    <a id="_1"></a>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Dancing</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                    	<li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The Registration Link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants are required to shoot their performance in 1080p and in landscape mode.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants have to introduce themselves before their performance.
                                                            <ul class="check-circle">
                                                               <li>For Eg: "My name is Dipesh Joshi, I am studying in B. Tech 3rd year at Amrapali Group of  Institutes Haldwani. I will be performing on Thal ki Bazar song." Participants may also introduce themselves in Hindi/ Kumaoni/ Garhwali.</li> 
                                                            </ul>
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>Video has to sent at agihld@gmail.com. And also mention your name and phone number in the mail. </li>
                                                        <li>The length of the video should be 3-5 minutes.</li>
                                                        <li>Use of Filters is not allowed.</li>

                                                    </ul>
                                                    <a id="_2">&nbsp;</a>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Singing/ Poetry/ Instruments</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                    	<li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The Registration Link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants are required to shoot their performance in 1080p  and in landscape mode.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants have to introduce themselves before their performance. 
                                                            <ul class="check-circle">
                                                                <li>For Eg: "My name is Dipesh Joshi, I am studying in B. Tech 3rd year at Amrapali Group of  Institutes Haldwani. I will be singing Thal ki Bazar song." Participants may also introduce themselves in Hindi/ Kumaoni/ Garhwali.</li>
                                                            </ul>
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>Participants may use Karaoke/ Background Music / Instrument Support during their performance. </li>
                                                        <li>Use of Voice Enhancers/ Filters is not permitted.</li>
                                                        <li>Video has to sent at agihld@gmail.com. And also mention your name and phone number in the mail.</li>
                                                        <li>Length of the video should be 2-4 minutes.</li>
                                                        <li>Students interested in Poetry may recite their own composition or poems by others. Acknowledgement has to be given in case the poem has been penned by some other poet.</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <a id="_3">&nbsp;</a>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Painting/ Sketching</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                        <li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The Registration Link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival.</li>
                                                        <li>HD Photographs of Painting/ Sketches have to be sent at agihld@gmail.com. Also mention your name and phone number in the mail.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants are requested to share 4 Photographs of their Work. These Photographs have to be taken at different stages of the Work.</li>
                                                        <li>Participants are also requested to share a brief description of their Work (60-100 Words)</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <a id="_4">&nbsp;</a>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Photography</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                        <li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The Registration Link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival.</li>
                                                        <li>HD Photographs have to be sent at agihld@gmail.com. Also mention your name and phone number in the mail.</li>
                                                        <li>Photographs may be related (but not restricted to) to Nature, Culture/ Cuisine of Uttarakhand, Religious/ Tourist Places etc</li>
                                                        <li>Participants are also requested to share a brief description/ Caption of their Photograph (60-100 Words)  </li>
                                                        <li>Basic Level of Editing is allowed.</li> 
                                                        <li>Participants have to submit a Photograph of themselves in the same frame.</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <a id="_5">&nbsp;</a>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Quiz</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                        <li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The registration link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival.</li>
                                                        <li>The Online Quiz shall comprise of 50 general awareness questions related to Uttarakhand.</li>
                                                        <li>Round 2 may be organised in case of Tie/ High Competition in Round 1.</li>
                                                        <li>Date and Timing of the Quiz shall be divulged to registered candidates only.</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <a id="_6">&nbsp;</a>
                                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <h3>Rules for <i class="activities">Essay/ Blog Writing</i></h3>
                                                    <ul class="check-square">
                                                        <li>Advance Registration is compulsory. The registration link is www.amrapali.ac.in/wintercarnival</li>
                                                        <li>Essay/ Blogs have to be sent at agihld@gmail.com. Also mention your name and phone number in the mail.</li>
                                                        <li>The Word Limit Essays/ Blogs shall be 500 words.</li>
                                                        <li>Essays/ Blogs may be written in Hindi or English</li>
                                                        <li>Essays/ Blogs have to be submitted in both Word and PDF Format.</li>
                                                        <li>Handwritten Essays have to be submitted in PDF Form.</li>
                                                        <li>Plagiarised essays/ blog shall not be considered.</li>
                                                        <li>In case a photograph, research has been used in the essay / blog, it should be properly referenced.</li>
                                                        <li>The Topics for Essay/ Blogs can be related (but not limited to) to the following 
                                                            <ul class="check-circle">
                                                                <li>History, Geography, General Awareness related to Uttarakhand</li>
                                                                <li>Famous Personalities from Uttarakhand</li>
                                                                <li>Tourism in Uttarakhand</li>
                                                                <li>Places of Religion Importance on Uttarakhand</li>
                                                                <li>Uttarakhand Movement</li>
                                                                <li>Social Issues like Migration/ Movements in Uttrakhand like Chipko Movement etc</li>
                                                                <li>Culture/ Cuisines of Uttarakhand</li>
                                                            </ul>
                                                        </li>
                                                        <span style="color: #0000ff"><b><i>Note</i></b>: Essays/ Blogs with Political/ Anti Establishment/ Religious- Social Hatred Agenda shall be rejected.</span>
                                                    </ul>
